〈'''Lonely Together'''〉是由瑞典[[唱片骑师|DJ]]兼[[音乐制作人|音乐制作人]][[艾维奇|艾维奇]]主唱，英国歌手[[瑞塔·奥拉|瑞塔·奥拉]]伴唱的歌曲。歌曲发行于2017年8月11日并作为艾维奇的[[迷你专辑|迷你专辑]]《[[Avīci_(01)|Avīci (01)]]》的第二首歌曲<ref>{{cite news|last=Baillie|first=Katie|date=2017-08-23|title=VIDEO EXCLUSIVE: Avicii continues return after two years with single featuring Rita Ora|url=http://metro.co.uk/2017/08/23/video-exclusive-avicii-continues-return-after-two-years-with-single-featuring-rita-ora-6869666/|work={{tsl|en|Metro (British newspaper)||Metro}}|accessdate=2017-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824093650/http://metro.co.uk/2017/08/23/video-exclusive-avicii-continues-return-after-two-years-with-single-featuring-rita-ora-6869666/|archive-date=2017-08-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年11月17日发行了混音EP版<ref name="Remixes EP" />。〈Lonely Together〉是艾维奇于2018年4月去世前发行的最后一首单曲<ref name="538Koningsdag">{{cite news|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8401374/rita-ora-avicii-lonely-together-tribute-538koningsdag-festival-netherlands|title=Rita Ora Sings 'Lonely Together' in Emotional Tribute to Avicii at Netherlands Festival|last=Iasimone|first=Ashley|date=2018-04-28|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|accessdate=2018-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180817193117/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8401374/rita-ora-avicii-lonely-together-tribute-538koningsdag-festival-netherlands|archive-date=2018-08-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==现场表演==
[[瑞塔·奥拉|瑞塔·奥拉]]在荷兰538 Koningsdag音乐节上演唱了〈Lonely Together〉，当时正值艾维奇去世一周。她将歌曲献给了这位DJ并进行了[[默哀|默哀]]<ref name="538Koningsdag"/>。5月27日，在{{le|BBC's Biggest Weekend|BBC Radio 1's Big Weekend}}上，她也向艾维奇表达了敬意<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-44273027|title=Biggest Weekend: Rita Ora's Avicii tribute|last=Savage|first=Mark|date=2018-05-27|work=BBC News|accessdate=2018-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180528205412/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-44273027|archive-date=2018-05-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/rita-ora-pays-emotional-tribute-avicii-bbcs-biggest-weekend-lonely-together-2326516|title=Rita Ora pays emotional tribute to Avicii at BBC's Biggest Weekend – NME|date=2018-05-27|work=NME|accessdate=2018-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180530112228/http://www.nme.com/news/music/rita-ora-pays-emotional-tribute-avicii-bbcs-biggest-weekend-lonely-together-2326516|archive-date=2018-05-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

